OL,3,CSchool, parks and toilets defaced with
OL,4,Cswastikas and offensive slurs
OL,6,FJersey's capital St Helier has been
OL,7,Fdefaced with dozens of swastikas and
OL,8,Fhighly offensive language.
OL,10,FAn all-girls primary school, public
OL,11,Fparks, a bus stop and toilets are
OL,12,Famong the places affected.
OL,14,FBenches, roads, bins, walls and
OL,15,Fpavements have all been targeted.
OL,17,FMuch of the graffiti is too extreme to
OL,18,Frepeat but includes racist and
OL,19,Fhomophobic slurs.
