OL,3,CSchool, parks and toilets defaced with
OL,4,Cswastikas and offensive slurs
OL,6,FTwo of the messages read, "N******
OL,7,FLEAVE NOW" and "STOP GAY PRIDE" next
OL,8,Fto swastikas. Another says, "MEN
OL,9,FDESERVE JUSTICE".
OL,11,FThe island's Chief Minister, Deputy
OL,12,FLyndon Farnham, says he is "deeply
OL,13,Fdisturbed" and has strongly condemned
OL,14,Fthe "cowardly and destructive act".
