OL,6,FJust two months ago, thousands
OL,7,Fgathered in Jersey and Guernsey to
OL,8,Fcelebrate Liberation Day - marking 80
OL,9,Fyears since the end of German rule.
OL,11,FThe States of Jersey Police says it is
OL,12,Finvestigating and reviewing CCTV
OL,13,Ffootage, with the first report made at
OL,14,F7:30am on Friday 11 July.
OL,16,FIt states "numerous logs regarding
OL,17,Foffensive graffiti" have been made,
OL,18,Fincluding at West Park, People's Park
OL,19,Fand Helvetia School - involving
OL,20,Fvehicles, buildings and general public
OL,21,Fareas.
